      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/jefferies-warns-of-slowing-equity-inflows-from-local-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group Inc.) 表示，随着市场回报率下降，流入印度股票共同基金的散户资金流面临减弱的风险。]]></description>
