    </item>
    <item>
      <title>强气旋在澳大利亚铁矿石枢纽附近登陆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/powerful-cyclone-set-to-hit-australia-s-iron-ore-hub-on-friday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[强气旋泽莉亚在澳大利亚铁矿石出口中心附近登陆，带来强降雨和破坏性阵风，该系统向内陆移动时对大型矿山和关键铁路连接构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/powerful-cyclone-set-to-hit-australia-s-iron-ore-hub-on-friday</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Feb 2025 00:03:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
